    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-08-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-08-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="60"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d60">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 704.6271</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Roumania</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_VCJ1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Vopicka</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucharest</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-08-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received August 29, 8.20 a.
                        m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>297. German Minister asked me this day to take charge of German interests in
                    Roumania, as Roumania is expected to go to war within a day or two joining
                    Entente powers. Have promised to comply with his request subject to the approval
                    of Department.</p>
                <p>A special conference was held at the Palace between the King, the Prime Minister
                    and his colleagues, representatives of all political parties and their
                    ex-ministers, and following this conference martial law has been proclaimed
                    throughout Roumania.</p>
                <pb facs="0334" n="48" xml:id="pg_48"/>
                <p>Please inform my wife, 3251 Washington Boulevard, Chicago, that owing to
                    conditions now prevailing here my leave of absence has been postponed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_VCJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vopicka</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
